  <div class="card">
  <h4 class="section-title">About Our Library</h4>
  <p>
    Our Library is a hub of knowledge and learning, providing access to thousands of resources that support students, educators, and researchers. We aim to foster a culture of reading, research, and intellectual growth.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h4 class="section-title">Library Mission</h4>
  <p>
    Our mission is to provide easy access to a wide range of books, digital media, and academic resources. We strive to promote literacy, encourage independent learning, and support academic success for all users.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h4 class="section-title">Key Features</h4>
  <ul>
    <li>📚 <strong>Vast Collection:</strong> Over 5000 books covering Literature, Science, Technology, History, and more.</li>
    <li>💻 <strong>Digital Resources:</strong> Access to e-books, research papers, online journals, and databases.</li>
    <li>🧑‍🏫 <strong>Supportive Staff:</strong> Friendly and knowledgeable librarians ready to assist with research and reading needs.</li>
    <li>💺 <strong>Reading Facilities:</strong> Quiet and comfortable reading areas for focused study.</li>
    <li>🔁 <strong>Book Lending System:</strong> Modern LMS platform to issue and return books quickly and efficiently.</li>
    <li>🕒 <strong>Operating Hours:</strong> Monday to Saturday – 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h4 class="section-title">Who Can Use the Library?</h4>
  <p>
    The library is open to students, faculty, and staff members. Users can register through the system to borrow books and access digital content. Special sessions are also conducted for new members on how to navigate the LMS.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h4 class="section-title">Future Plans</h4>
  <p>
    We are constantly evolving! Upcoming features include mobile app integration, personalized book suggestions, and expanding our digital archive for remote learners.
  </p>
